OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,FGalloway and West Dumfries covers
OL,7,Ftowns including Stranraer, Newton
OL,8,FStewart, Kirkcudbright Castle Douglas
OL,9,Fand the western side of Dumfries.
OL,11,FThe seat has been held by the
OL,12,FConservatives since it was created in
OL,13,F2011.
OL,15,FITV Border has interviewed the main
OL,16,Fcandidates.
OL,18,FThe Reform candidate for Galloway and
OL,19,FWest Dumfries instantly came under the
OL,20,Fspotlight when she was selected for
OL,21,Fcontroversial social media activity.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
