OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777216266
OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,FSenga Beresford replied "Me," to a
OL,7,Fpost on the social media site X from
OL,8,FAshlea Simon, the deputy leader of the
OL,9,Ffar-right party Britain First, which
OL,10,Fsaid: "In the UK Muslims are demanding
OL,11,Fthat sharia law is implemented. I
OL,12,Fdemand that we deport the lot of them.
OL,13,FWho's with me?"
OL,15,FShe told ITV Border: "I can only
OL,16,Fapologise if people have
OL,17,Fmisunderstood. I looked up sharia law
OL,18,Fand it doesn't comply with our law."
OL,26,@nD@YOUnD@]O]rD@GOUuD@OO]wD@VOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777216266
OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,FAsked if she thought Muslims want to
OL,7,Fbring in sharia law, Ms Beresford
OL,8,Ftwice said: "That's what the post
OL,9,Fsaid."
OL,11,FShe added: "Muslim communities, I
OL,12,Fcertainly do not want to do that
OL,13,F(deport them) and I have nothing
OL,14,Fagainst Muslims."
OL,16,FMs Beresford has also been criticised
OL,17,Ffor social media posts backing the far-
OL,18,Fright activist Tommy Robinson.
OL,26,@pD@MOUqD@FO]sD@LOUuD@ApmuD@MpnvD@QO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
