PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777216266
OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,FAsked about those messages, she said:
OL,7,F"I don't know him personally, right. I
OL,8,Fdon't follow him. What I would say
OL,9,Fabout him is we should be grateful for
OL,10,Fthe fact that he brought the grooming
OL,11,Fgangs inquiry to light."
OL,13,FRobinson, whose real name is Stephen
OL,14,FYaxley-Lennon, was jailed for
OL,15,Finterfering with the trial of a sexual
OL,16,Fgrooming gang at Leeds Crown Court in
OL,17,F2018.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/18
