OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,FMs Beresford said she is standing for
OL,7,Felection because she feels "we have
OL,8,Fbeen let down so badly by previous
OL,9,Fgovernments".
OL,11,FScottish Conservative
OL,13,FFinlay Carson has been the MSP for
OL,14,Fthis seat for a decade after replacing
OL,15,Fhis Scottish Conservative predecessor,
OL,16,Fthe late Alex Fergusson, in 2016.
OL,18,FHe said: "I think I've been a strong
OL,19,Fvoice. Not coming from a political
OL,20,Fbackground but a background in
OL,21,Fagriculture."
OL,26,@oD@\OUqD@LO]zD@JOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
