OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,FMr Carson said that retaining NHS
OL,7,Fworkers is one of the key issues
OL,8,Ffacing the constituency.
OL,10,FChallenged on whether he'd be able to
OL,11,Fachieve this, he said: "We've just got
OL,12,Fto look at what happened a few weeks
OL,13,Fago. John Swinney came down to speak
OL,14,Fto trainee nurses in Dumfries and was
OL,15,Fall very friendly with them.
OL,17,F"What he didn't realise was that my
OL,18,Ffootage is absolutely full of emails
OL,19,Ffrom these trainee nurses who do the
OL,20,Fwork here and then there's no jobs for
OL,21,Fthem.
OL,26,@sD@XOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777216266
OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,F"So it's not a shortage of workers
OL,7,Fwhen it comes to some nurses. It's
OL,8,Fworkplace conditions, it's about
OL,9,Fensuring these nurses have full-time
OL,10,Fjobs and don't end up in the nursing
OL,11,Fbank with uncertainty."
OL,13,FEmma Harper missed out on this
OL,14,Fconstituency, finishing runner up in
OL,15,F2021, but was elected as an SNP MSP on
OL,16,Fthe South Scotland list.
OL,18,FBefore that, she was a nurse for 30
OL,19,Fyears.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/18
