OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,FThere has been intense criticism of
OL,7,Fthe failure to upgrade the A75 and A77
OL,8,Froads but Ms Harper said progress is
OL,9,Fbeing made by her party in government.
OL,11,F"I've been on my feet in chamber in
OL,12,Fvarious debates and questions as well,
OL,13,Fraising the issues around how
OL,14,Fimportant economically the A75 is
OL,15,Facross our region.
OL,17,F"Oh there's been a lot happening. I
OL,18,Fgot a recent letter from Fiona Hyslop
OL,19,Fbefore dissolution.
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@AOU
