OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,F"She's the cabinet secretary for
OL,7,Ftransport, laying out how many
OL,8,Fmillions have been spent investing in
OL,9,Fthe road.
OL,11,F"The Springholm/Crocketford bypass is
OL,12,Fin design process right now and that's
OL,13,Fsomething that I think the people
OL,14,Facross Galloway are welcoming."
OL,16,FScottish Labour
