OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,FJack McConnel is one "L" away from
OL,7,Fsharing a name with the last person
OL,8,Ffrom his party to serve as first
OL,9,Fminister, Lord McConnell of
OL,10,FGlenscorrodale.
OL,12,FThe younger Mr McConnel, a former
OL,13,Fdiplomat, said he agrees with the
OL,14,Fdecision of his current party leader,
OL,15,FAnas Sarwar, to call for Sir Keir
OL,16,FStarmer to quit as prime minister.
OL,26,@nD@VOUnD@XO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
