OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,FHolyrood polling has suggested
OL,7,FScottish Labour's popularity has
OL,8,Ftanked in line with people's
OL,9,Fdissatisfaction with the UK
OL,10,Fgovernment, leaving the party lagging
OL,11,Fbehind the SNP.
OL,13,FLabour finished third in 2021, almost
OL,14,F12,000 votes behind the SNP in second.
OL,16,FMr McConnel said: "I think the most
OL,17,Funfortunate thing about the UK Labour
OL,18,Fgovernment is it has been bad at
OL,19,Fcommunicating the good things it's
OL,20,Fbeen doing.
OL,26,@xD@SOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777216266
OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,F"But now we're falling into the SNP
OL,7,Ftrap of talking about Keir Starmer and
OL,8,Fnot Scotland. Of course he's unpopular
OL,9,Fbut the lucky thing is it's about
OL,10,FScotland, about John Swinney or Anas
OL,11,FSarwar."
OL,13,FScottish Liberal Democrats
OL,15,FIn 2021, the Liberal Democrat
OL,16,Fcandidate lost their deposit by
OL,17,Ffinishing last of the major parties
OL,18,Fand only collecting 948 votes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
