CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777216266
OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,FBut this year's hopeful Tracey Warman
OL,7,Finsisted she is confident that she can
OL,8,Fupset the applecart and do well in
OL,9,Fthis election.
OL,11,FKey to this, she said, would be
OL,12,Fbringing a human and personal touch to
OL,13,Fcampaigning.
OL,15,FShe said: "I'm not interested in the
OL,16,Fhuge big party lines but I am
OL,17,Finterested in people.
OL,19,F"I'm very confident. I'm very, very
OL,20,Fconfident. I'm a new face, I'm not a
OL,21,Fpolitician.
OL,26,@wD@KOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
