PN,35714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777216266
OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,F"I know I'm standing as a politician
OL,7,Fbut me, as a person, I'm not a
OL,8,Fpolitician. I just strongly believe
OL,9,Fthat we can do better and we deserve
OL,10,Fto do better for our local people."
OL,12,FFull list of candidates standing in
OL,13,FGalloway and West Dumfries
OL,15,FKey issues for voters in Galloway and
OL,16,FWest Dumfries
OL,18,FThe failure to upgrade the A75 has led
OL,19,Fto a series of complaints about safety
OL,20,Fand the negative economic impact of
OL,21,Fthe current state of the road.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@cO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/18
