OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,FExpectant mothers have to travel more
OL,7,Fthan 70 miles along the route for
OL,8,Ftheir babies to be delivered in
OL,9,FDumfries because of a lack of local
OL,10,Fmaternity services.
OL,12,FGina Clive, from Stranraer, gave birth
OL,13,Fto her daughter Nieve at a farm road
OL,14,Fend in Dunraggit in August 2016.
OL,16,FShe said: "So when the ambulance
OL,17,Fdriver pulled the blanket over he was
OL,18,Flike, 'Don't panic! Don't panic!'. And
OL,19,Fhe took everything off and there she
OL,20,Fwas.
OL,26,@xD@KOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777216266
OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,F"It happened so fast, I never even
OL,7,Fthought that could be a possibility."
OL,9,FThankfully her daughter Neive is now a
OL,10,Fhealthy and happy nine year old.
OL,12,FNHS Dumfries and Galloway said
OL,13,Fpreviously it cannot comment on
OL,14,Findividual cases but stressed that the
OL,15,Fwelfare of mothers and children is the
OL,16,Fprimary concern of the midwifery team.
OL,18,FAny plans for the unit would also only
OL,19,Fschedule, low-risk births with travel
OL,20,Fto Dumfries still being required for
OL,21,Fthe majority.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@eO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
