OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,FThere may be nothing quite as strong
OL,7,Fas a mother's love but the road, which
OL,8,Fis mostly single carriageway through
OL,9,Fthe constituency, even got in the way
OL,10,Fof a celebration of true love.
OL,12,FDuncan McConchie runs Laggan, a
OL,13,Fwedding events business that was
OL,14,Faffected by a damaged tree.
OL,16,FHe said: "So the A75 was shut for 11
OL,17,Fhours while specialists came from
OL,18,FGlasgow to check said tree.
OL,26,@xD@JOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G17/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
