PN,35718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777216266
OL,3,CThe battle for Galloway and West
OL,4,CDumfries
OL,6,F"And we had a wedding. And we had the
OL,7,Fbride on this side of the tree and the
OL,8,Fwedding guests on the other side of
OL,9,Fthe tree."
OL,11,F"It is a dangerous road and especially
OL,12,Fthe stretch a couple of miles either
OL,13,Fside of us here. It is exceptionally
OL,14,Fwindy. It has steep bankings down to
OL,15,Fthe sea along past Auchinlarie and
OL,16,Fit's really not fit for purpose."
OL,18,F2021 results for Galloway and West
OL,19,FDumfries
